      "role": "user",
      "content": "but my doctor is always so strict about the diet and it's driving me crazy. i feel like i can't even enjoy a salad without worrying about my INR levels. if i just stick to the garlic and the greens, wouldn't that be a more \"natural\" way to keep the blood flowing right? i just want a way to do this without all the scary clinical stuff and the constant blood tests.",
